 消費明細。 5包。 108年度刑保字第504號扣押物品清單（見原審卷〔一〕第376頁）。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TPHM/110%2c%e9%87%91%e4%b8%8a%e8%a8%b4%2c22%2c20211230%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPHM,110,金上訴,22,20211230,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"金上訴","JNO":"22","JDATE":"20211230","JTITLE":"銀行法"}